column14: 7. Do you frequently use the TTC?
column15: If you answered no to above question, why not?  [I have access to other transportation services that serve me well]

column25: 8. In the past year, have you had to delay home repairs or modifications because they were unaffordable? [A major home repair such as a new roof, furnace, or plumbing or electrical problems?]
